---
// FounderBridge — narrative bridge between pain and solution
// A single honest paragraph in the founder's voice
---

<div class="founder-bridge">
  <div class="founder-bridge__inner">
    <p class="founder-bridge__quote">
      "I built StreamLoop because I spent two years staring at my analytics and having no idea what to change. Not because I wasn't trying — but because no one told me what the &nbsp;<em>one thing</em>&nbsp; was."
    </p>
    <p class="founder-bridge__pivot">
      StreamLoop gives you &nbsp;<em>one thing</em>&nbsp; to fix. Just one. After every stream.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .founder-bridge {
    padding: 80px 24px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .founder-bridge__inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .founder-bridge__quote {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #adadb8;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.1s both;
  }

  .founder-bridge__quote em,
  .founder-bridge__pivot em {
    color: #c4a4ff;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .founder-bridge__pivot {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.4vw, 1.35rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #efeff1;
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.3s both;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .founder-bridge__quote,
    .founder-bridge__pivot {
      animation: none;
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
</style>
